   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy.optimize import minimize"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 41,
   "id": "02ec7cf9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000x600 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "\n",
    "np.random.seed(16)\n",
    "coefficients = np.random.randint(-10, 11, size=6)\n",
    "polynomial = np.poly1d(coefficients)\n",
    "x_values = np.linspace(-5, 5, 1000)\n",
    "y_values = polynomial(x_values)\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "plt.plot(x_values, y_values, label='Polynomial')\n",
    "res_max = minimize(lambda x: -polynomial(x), 0, bounds=[(-5, 5)])\n",
    "res_min = minimize(lambda x: polynomial(x), 0, bounds=[(-5, 5)])\n",
    "plt.scatter([res_max.x[0], res_min.x[0]], [polynomial(res_max.x[0]), polynomial(res_min.x[0])], color='red')\n",
    "plt.text(res_max.x[0], polynomial(res_max.x[0]), f'Max: ({res_max.x[0]:.2f}, {polynomial(res_max.x[0]):.2f})', fontsize=10, ha='right')\n",
    "plt.text(res_min.x[0], polynomial(res_min.x[0]), f'Min: ({res_min.x[0]:.2f}, {polynomial(res_min.x[0]):.2f})', fontsize=10, ha='right')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('x')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('y')\n",
    "plt.title('Plot of a 5th Degree Polynomial with Annotated Extrema')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "plt.show()\n"
   ]
  },
